{"tid":370351,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴大膽變革！廢曼聯十年鐵則 獲球員力撐","createTime":"2017-08-23T03:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T15:35:19.000Z","uid":8968,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2f68d256a754d96a2df48a577dd080ff594c799c","tid":370351,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:30:11.000Z","msg":"　　自攻入主曼聯後，摩連奴在球隊管理方面一直比較溫和。來自《每日郵報》的最新消息稱，摩帥如今又做了一項變革。他允許球員在主場比賽前待在家裡陪伴家人，而不是球隊在酒店集體度過。顯然，摩帥是希望給球員更多的信任。<br />\n<br />\n　　按照傳統，在奧脫福的主場比賽前一天晚上，曼聯球員需要集體入住曼徹斯特的勞里酒店。不過摩帥做出了改變，如果是週末的比賽，曼聯將允許球員在週六晚上留在家裡陪伴伴侶和家人。週日，球隊再集結一起吃飯和進行球隊會議。本週六曼聯主場對陣李斯特城的比賽，這套新程序就將開始實施。<br />\n<br />\n　　曼聯在主場比賽前，球隊要在五星酒店一起過夜的規定已經延續了超過10年了，從費格遜時代開始就是如此。莫耶斯和雲高爾時代，這個規定也在繼續，雲高爾甚至製定了10點半必須就寢的規定。但是摩連奴相信新的規定可以讓球員更好的從家庭中收益，他也相信球員們會為比賽做好正確的準備。當然新政策的效果還有待檢驗，曼聯的球員們也已經被告知，球隊會關注他們的情況，確保不會有球員破壞規矩。<br />\n<br />\n　　大部分球員對於摩帥的新規都很支持，但是也有一些球員對此持保留態度，他們擔憂這會導致球隊過於放鬆。曼聯目前和酒店還有2年的合約<span style=\"color: red;\">，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如今只有摩連奴一個人住在酒店了</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\nDaddy <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔反了"},{"pid":"719607fe8e4456360a25de63fddc6ba54e7273ca","tid":370351,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"下年就會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4068f6a53837e406fd682be90e5bb20e0f9295","tid":370351,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:50:06.000Z","msg":"同老婆扑野扑到腳軟"},{"pid":"007472dfdbc370a1485948797c71df7d02c115db","tid":370351,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T07:53:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下年就會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主今年已經仆定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d314b9ad46f96f67234b9f6b90a1d83cc161529e","tid":370351,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下年就會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主今年已經仆定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDiulelomo dandandada"},{"pid":"88cd5e43a9d8aeed749e9ef7775fa42a657efdeb","tid":370351,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T08:26:18.000Z","msg":"今季曼真係好有冠軍相<br />\n相反轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85db683c5a3f2736b6a698c190d1647376bcd1fb","tid":370351,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T11:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>下年就會仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主今年已經仆定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDiulelomo dandandada</blockquote><br />\n講到出面<br />\n都只係dandandada<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"4b50e2db24f8bdfcbd88494f8c4c97fb4834df46","tid":370351,"uid":12980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同老婆扑野扑到腳軟</blockquote><br />\n你都on9<br />\n仲扑老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a199c1969b76bc5479ebf07ee001cfd50fd2a52","tid":370351,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T01:06:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同老婆扑野扑到腳軟</blockquote><br />\n你都on9<br />\n仲扑老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400aa9c01e2e4a3f53889f9f525d544ec1a78557","tid":370351,"uid":63233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep